James Jordan, 44, was every inch the proud husband as he showed off his wife Ola’s weight loss journey on social media. The Strictly Come Dancing star took to Twitter to share a video of Ola wearing a number of bikinis during a photoshoot. In the behind-the-scenes video, Ola could be seen posing up a storm as she modelled various bikinis that varied in shape and colour. Along with the clip, James penned a heartfelt caption - praising his wife in view of his 340,000 followers. He wrote: “Wow!! How amazing does she look?! Proud doesn’t even cover it.”